OL,3,CIRA Spy Denis Donaldson 'a victim of
OL,4,Cconflict,' Gerry Adams tells court
OL,6,FThe hearing revolves around a BBC
OL,7,FSpotlight documentary aired in 2016
OL,8,Fand a subsequent online article which
OL,9,Fboth contained an anonymous source
OL,10,Falleging that the former Sinn Fein
OL,11,Fpresident sanctioned Denis Donaldson's
OL,12,Fkilling.
OL,14,FHe was found dead in a rural Co
OL,15,FDonegal cottage in 2006, the year
OL,16,Fafter he confessed to working as a
OL,17,FBritish agent.
