OL,3,CIRA Spy Denis Donaldson 'a victim of
OL,4,Cconflict,' Gerry Adams tells court
OL,6,FThe court previously heard that he
OL,7,Fconfessed to senior Sinn Fein
OL,8,Fofficials about his role working for
OL,9,Fsecurity intelligence.
OL,11,FGerry Adams told the court: "Denis
OL,12,F(Donaldson) became an administrator at
OL,13,FSinn Fein in Stormont. I liked the guy
OL,14,Fand I knew him, I knew his wife and
OL,15,Fhis daughter but I didn't actually
OL,16,Fhave any dealings with him even though
OL,17,Four relationship was a good
OL,18,Frelationship."
