OL,3,CIRA Spy Denis Donaldson 'a victim of
OL,4,Cconflict,' Gerry Adams tells court
OL,6,FMr Adams also told the court that he
OL,7,Fwas working at a 'different level' to
OL,8,FMr Donaldson in the early 2000s.
OL,10,FIn 2002, Sinn Fein offices at Stormont
OL,11,Fwere raided concerning spying
OL,12,Fallegations. However it was in 2005
OL,13,Fwhen Mr Donaldson's confession came to
OL,14,Flight.
OL,16,FA jury will decide if Mr Adams'
OL,17,Freputation has been damaged with the
OL,18,Fhearing set to last around four weeks.
