OL,6,FDuring Wednesday's evidence, Mr Adams
OL,7,Falso recounted the years leading up to
OL,8,Fthe signing of the Good Friday
OL,9,FAgreement which he is recognised as
OL,10,Fbeing a key negotiator in.
OL,12,FOpening the case on Tuesday, barrister
OL,13,Ffor Mr Adams Tom Hogan SC said the
OL,14,Freputation of Mr Adams as a
OL,15,F"peacemaker" suffered an "unjustified"
OL,16,Fattack due to the broadcast of the BBC
OL,17,Fprogramme.
