OL,6,FAt the end of the day, Mr Adams
OL,7,Fentered the witness box and described
OL,8,Fhis early political awakenings in
OL,9,FBelfast in the 1960s.
OL,11,FContinuing his evidence on Wednesday,
OL,12,FMr Adams told the court he first met
OL,13,FMr Donaldson in H-11 in Long Kesh.
OL,15,FHe said Mr Donaldson was not an
OL,16,Finternee and was a sentenced prisoner
OL,17,Fwho "had been there a long time".
