OL,3,CIRA Spy Denis Donaldson 'a victim of
OL,4,Cconflict,' Gerry Adams tells court
OL,6,FHe told the court he was not sure what
OL,7,FMr Donaldson did after his release,
OL,8,Fbut believed he did some
OL,9,F"international work" before becoming
OL,10,Fan administrator for Sinn Fein's
OL,11,FStormont team.
OL,13,FHe said that in 2002, a convoy of RUC
OL,14,FLand Rovers arrived at Stormont,
OL,15,Fraided the Sinn Fein office and
OL,16,Farrested Mr Donaldson and others.
OL,18,FThe arrests were made in relation to a
OL,19,Fclaim of a republican spy-ring at
OL,20,FStormont, which Mr Adams said was
OL,21,F"complete nonsense".
