OL,3,CIRA Spy Denis Donaldson 'a victim of
OL,4,Cconflict,' Gerry Adams tells court
OL,6,FAfter IRA de-commissioning took place
OL,7,Fin the summer of 2005, he said Mr
OL,8,FDonaldson and others who had been
OL,9,Farrested had the charges against them
OL,10,Fdropped in November.
OL,12,F"But quite quickly after the charges
OL,13,Fwere dropped it was revealed that he
OL,14,Fwas an agent."
OL,16,FMr Adams told the court: "Denis
OL,17,FDonaldson got a visit from the PSNI
OL,18,Fand he was given a piece of paper that
OL,19,Falerted him to the fact that he was
OL,20,Fgoing to be named as an agent.
